```onclick="clicked({{date.product_1_price}}, {{date.prod_date}})"```
and the actual function:
```function clicked(price, dateTime){
  console.log(price);

}```
but upon click, I get :

```booksnap:2068 Uncaught ReferenceError: clicked is not defined
